ðŸ”¥ METHOD 2: CLONE THE REPO (For GitHub Users)
Step 1: Clone Your GitHub Repo
batch

cd Desktop
git clone https://github.com/YourUsername/YourRepoName.git
Step 2: Go Into The Folder
batch

