ðŸŽ¯ METHOD 3: ONE-CLICK BAT FILE (From GitHub)
Create this BAT file on your Desktop:
File: Download and Run Scanner.bat

batch

@echo off
title Downloading Security Scanner from GitHub
color 0A

echo.
echo ============================================
echo   DOWNLOADING FROM GITHUB...
echo ============================================
echo.

REM Change this to YOUR GitHub URL
set GITHUB_URL=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YourUsername/YourRepo/main/SecurityScanner.py

echo Downloading script...
curl -o "%USERPROFILE%\Desktop\SecurityScanner.py" %GITHUB_URL%

echo.
echo Installing requirements...
pip install customtkinter psutil

echo.
echo Starting Security Scanner...
python "%USERPROFILE%\Desktop\SecurityScanner.py"

pause
